{"tid":21183,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"加州迪士尼有200隻流浪貓！","createTime":"2016-12-03T16:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T15:22:14.000Z","uid":29314,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b5cbc8313cba8e894708559ed17ddbc416a98ef","tid":21183,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:55:32.000Z","msg":"被海洋公園視為大麻煩的流浪貓，若能生活在美國加州迪士尼樂園可能幸福得多，皆因樂園將流浪貓視為「員工」之一，不單准牠們自由來去，更聘有護理員專門照顧、幫忙絕育，貓咪們不單會在夜裡幫忙捉老鼠和驅趕害蟲，甚至吸引到「貓奴」入場賞貓，成為樂園另類景點，達到雙贏。<br />\n<br />\n其實加州迪士尼1955年開幕後不久，園內已出現流浪貓的身影，至今估數量超過200隻貓。樂園除了為牠們絕育，還有專人為牠們定期檢查，並在園內劃出5個遠離遊人的餵食點，讓貓咪們能不受滋擾地進餐。迪士尼甚至為流浪貓們開設Twitter和名為「disneylandcats」的instagram帳號，專門收集遊客在樂園內追蹤野貓的「集郵成功」，每次有新相上載都吸引到大批愛貓之人留言讚好。"},{"pid":"d2567f55784187531464fbddee01f308559dcc93","tid":21183,"uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20161203/large/1480768059_019b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161203%2Flarge%2F1480768059_019b.jpg&h=93d59580&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1dba12ba503e468a45cd06caa8c56ac40322c342","tid":21183,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:58:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20161203/large/1480768072_b20f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161203%2Flarge%2F1480768072_b20f.jpg&h=767e89c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"827188acef4afd16739f4d4b3457bc147e04f1ca","tid":21183,"uid":25354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T17:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2d4777905f620d7f2001848bf830fdcc06a03a","tid":21183,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep